{
  "title": "Intensely Resinous German Fromage-Blanc Gratin",
  "description": "A plant-based German dish featuring fromage-blanc, with a resinous and glassy-jelly texture, served on a cedar plank. This meal-prep friendly recipe is perfect for a unique dinner experience.",
  "cuisine": "German",
